data.description: Don't miss out on this Charming Central Spokane Rancher. There is so much potential to make this feel like your own! This bright 4 bed, 2 bath home includes updates of fresh paint and laminate flooring throughout. Upstairs on the main level, you'll find the kitchen, spacious living room with fireplace, 2 bedrooms, and bath. Down the stairs into the basement, you'll enter the finished second main living space equipped with a fireplace built into a beautiful brick wall that is a short walk away from the laundry, additional (non-conforming) bedrooms, and bath perfect for an in-law suite. Back upstairs, you'll find french doors that lead you out to the backyard and a covered patio thats perfect for entertaining as well as the built-in storage underneath - for all of outdoor toys. This home offers a 2 car garage in addition to the 2 car parking out front. Close to Down River Grill, Audubon area, Bowl and Pitcher for hiking, and not far from North Mall or Downtown Spokane.
